reviewText: when Ayane starts a job as a maid in Kazuto's house her first task to greet the master. so when Ayane goes into Kazuto's room he mistakes her for Momiji. Ayane then learns that it is Momiji's morning job wake Kazuto up and watching this makes Ayane jealous because Kazuto is paying more attention to Momiji then her. Kazuto then tells the two girl to have a compaction and the winner will be rewarded. a few days later Kazuto takes Momiji to the amusement park. Kazuto gets bored after a while, until he sees the fairies wheel. while ride Kazuto sees the appeal and he and Momiji start to have his type of fun. when they get home Momiji save the fairies wheel ticket as proof that Kazuto can be kind.
From the very beginning, this fragile girl is sweet and desperate to please her rapist/lover.  You feel sorry for her and can't wait to see more.  It will turn you on if you are in to kink.
